high_descs: Go to the island across from the sink.
Pick up the butter knife on the island.
Face the center of the island.
Slice the potato on the island.
Turn around to the sink.
Put the butter knife in the sink.
Turn around to the island.
Pick up a slice of potato on the island.
Go to the microwave.
Cook the potato in the microwave.
Move over to the sink.
Put the cooked potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go across the room, turn left and go to the island counter on the left.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Move left to the potato on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn back around to the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Go left and around the island counter to the microwave.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave and pick it back up.
Turn left, go back around the counter and to the sink.
Put the slice of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the sink.

take the knife to the sink

approach the sliced potato
